Package: competitiontoolbox
Type: Package
Title: Additional Tools for Antitrust and Trade Practitioners
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Charles Taragin and Paulette Wolak
Maintainer: Charles Taragin <ctaragin@ftc.gov>
Depends: R (>= 2.10), antitrust (>= 0.99.11), trade (>= 0.5.4), shiny, rhandsontable
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr
Description: A shiny interface for both trade and antitrust. 
    The shiny interface provides users with the ability to calibrate 
    and simulate horizontal mergers using different supply and demand 
    models as well as the simulate the effects of tariffs.
License: Unlimited
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
